title: Shaq, Kenny and Chuck React to James Harden Being Traded to the Brooklyn Nets | NBA on TNT
author: NBA on TNT
description:
The Inside guys discuss the blockbuster deal that sent Rockets superstar James Harden to the Brooklyn Nets to join Kevin Durant and Kyrie Irving. 

Watch highlights from Inside the NBA with Shaq, Charles Barkley, Kenny Smith and Ernie Johnson and more! Subscribe now to be updated on the latest videos: https://www.youtube.com/nbaontnt?sub_confirmation=1
